---
---

<section id="experience" class="section">
  <p class="section-label">Experience</p>
  <h2 class="section-heading">Where I've worked.</h2>

  <div class="timeline">

    <div class="role">
      <div class="role-header">
        <h3 class="role-title">Senior Software Engineer</h3>
        <span class="role-company">Cox Automotive</span>
        <span class="role-dates">2021 &mdash; Present</span>
      </div>
      <div class="role-highlights">
        <div class="highlight cmyk-border-subtle">
          <h4 class="highlight-name">AI Agent for Enterprise CRM</h4>
          <p class="highlight-desc">Conversational AI agent enabling natural language CRM queries and actions on one of the automotive industry's largest datasets. Function calling via AWS Strands Agents for autonomous operation selection.</p>
          <span class="highlight-stack">Python &middot; AWS Strands Agents</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight cmyk-border-subtle">
          <h4 class="highlight-name">MCP Developer Platform</h4>
          <p class="highlight-desc">MCP tools enabling AI coding assistants to interact with Rally project management, adopted across hundreds of internal engineering teams.</p>
          <span class="highlight-stack">TypeScript &middot; Bun &middot; Node.js &middot; Zod</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight cmyk-border-subtle">
          <h4 class="highlight-name">Direct Mail Automation Platform</h4>
          <p class="highlight-desc">Led end-to-end development of direct mail API and React dashboard. Built CI/CD from scratch, integrated Lob API, resolved critical race condition blocking production release.</p>
          <span class="highlight-stack">TypeScript &middot; AWS CDK &middot; React &middot; Next.js</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="role">
      <div class="role-header">
        <h3 class="role-title">React Native Developer</h3>
        <span class="role-company">Alpine Media Technology</span>
        <span class="role-dates">2020 &mdash; 2021</span>
      </div>
      <div class="role-highlights">
        <div class="highlight cmyk-border-subtle">
          <h4 class="highlight-name">Mobile App Platform</h4>
          <p class="highlight-desc">Maintained app generator and CMS-driven theming engine producing branded iOS and Android apps for major ski resorts. Managed client onboarding and App Store release cycles.</p>
          <span class="highlight-stack">React Native</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .role {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .role-header {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .role-title {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .role-company {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--cmyk-magenta);
    margin-bottom: 0.1rem;
  }

  .role-dates {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }

  .role-highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 8px;
    filter: saturate(0%);
    transition: filter 0.5s ease;
  }

  .highlight:hover {
    filter: saturate(100%);
  }

  .highlight-name {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .highlight-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .highlight-stack {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  }
</style>
